-- Dan's Papers Publisher Allowed by Judge to Sell Most Assets to Insiders
-- Don Jeffrey
-- 2010-07-29T22:04:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/dan-s-papers-publisher-allowed-by-judge-to-sell-most-assets-to-insiders.html

          
          
             The sale of Brown Publishing Co.,
the owner of Dan’s Papers in New York’s Hamptons, to insiders
was approved by a bankruptcy judge.  
 U.S. Bankruptcy Judge Dorothy Eisenberg ruled today that
Brown Media, controlled by the publisher’s three top executives,
can acquire most of its assets for $22.4 million in cash.  
